name: reduce_lt6xbh
jaxpr:
{ lambda ; a:f32[2,4]. let
    b:f32[2,4] = neg a
    c:f32[2,4] = exp b
    d:f32[2,4] = add 1.0:f32[] c
    e:f32[2,4] = div -1.0:f32[] d
    f:f32[] = reduce_min[axes=(0, 1)] e
  in (f,) }

    %5 = stablehlo.divide %4, %3 : tensor<2x4xf32>

    %6 = stablehlo.reduce(%5 init: %cst_1) applies stablehlo.minimum across dimensions = [0, 1] : (tensor<2x4xf32>, tensor<f32>) -> tensor<f32>
